contents.en: You finally arrived on the first planet!
contents.ja: You finally arrived on the first planet!
contents.zh: You finally arrived on the first planet!

contents.en: It's an honor to be with you on the 'Laviah Project' to investigate all the stars on planet Laviah!
contents.ko:
행성 라비아의 모든 별을 조사하는 
'라비아 프로젝트'에 함께 하게 되어 영광이에요!
contents.ja: It's an honor to be with you on the 'Laviah Project' to investigate all the stars on planet Laviah!
contents.zh: It's an honor to be with you on the 'Laviah Project' to investigate all the stars on planet Laviah!

contents.en: Let us work together to fulfill our mission !!
contents.ko: 우리 함께 힘내서 임무를 수행 하도록 해요!!
contents.ja: Let us work together to fulfill our mission !!
contents.zh: Let us work together to fulfill our mission !!

contents.en: It's an ice crystal floating around the planet.
contents.ja: It's an ice crystal floating around the planet.
contents.zh: It's an ice crystal floating around the planet.

contents.en: You have to investigate the stars while avoiding them.
contents.ja: You have to investigate the stars while avoiding them.
contents.zh: You have to investigate the stars while avoiding them.

contents.en: Pressing and holding the screen can be avoided in the opposite direction.
contents.ko: 화면을 길게 누르면 반대 방향으로 피할 수 있어요.
contents.ja: Pressing and holding the screen can be avoided in the opposite direction.
contents.zh: Pressing and holding the screen can be avoided in the opposite direction.

contents.en: Large ice crystals are so fast that I'll mark them as light before they fall.
contents.ko: 큰 얼음 결정은 아주 빠르니까 떨어지기 전에 라이트로 표시해 둘게요.
contents.ja: Large ice crystals are so fast that I'll mark them as light before they fall.
contents.zh: Large ice crystals are so fast that I'll mark them as light before they fall.

contents.en: Be aware that when a light is displayed, a large crystal will be fall.
contents.ko: 라이트가 표시되면 큰 결정이 떨어진다는 점을 꼭 기억해두세요.
contents.ja: Be aware that when a light is displayed, a large crystal will be fall.
contents.zh: Be aware that when a light is displayed, a large crystal will be fall.

contents.en:
Oh! 
There are hard crystals that do not melt easily even after falling to the ground.
contents.ko:
아참! 
땅에 떨어지고 난 후에도 쉽게 녹지 않는 단단한 결정들도 있어요.
contents.ja:
Oh! 
There are hard crystals that do not melt easily even after falling to the ground.
contents.zh:
Oh! 
There are hard crystals that do not melt easily even after falling to the ground.

contents.en: Please be careful not to touch the body.
contents.ko: 꼭 몸에 닿지 않게 주의 하세요.
contents.ja: Please be careful not to touch the body.
contents.zh: Please be careful not to touch the body.

contents.en:
By the way, 
Because of the unstable earth, the ice will rise from the ground, so be careful.
contents.ko:
아참참! 
불안정한 대지 때문에 땅에서 얼음이 솟아나기도 하니까 조심 해야해요.
contents.ja:
By the way, 
Because of the unstable earth, the ice will rise from the ground, so be careful.
contents.zh:
By the way, 
Because of the unstable earth, the ice will rise from the ground, so be careful.

contents.en:
Oh! 
It's a star we have to investigate!!
contents.ja:
Oh! 
It's a star we have to investigate!!
contents.zh:
Oh! 
It's a star we have to investigate!!

contents.en: The more stars you get, the higher your exploration score.
contents.ja: The more stars you get, the higher your exploration score.
contents.zh: The more stars you get, the higher your exploration score.

contents.en: If you get stars continuously, your combo will increase.
contents.ja: If you get stars continuously, your combo will increase.
contents.zh: If you get stars continuously, your combo will increase.

contents.en: The higher the combo, the higher the score of a single exploration.
contents.ko: 콤보가 높으면 별 한개의 탐험점수가 높아져요.
contents.ja: The higher the combo, the higher the score of a single exploration.
contents.zh: The higher the combo, the higher the score of a single exploration.

contents.en: If you do not get the stars for a certain time, the combo will be cut off.
contents.ko: 일정시간 별을 얻지 않으면 콤보가 끊기니까 주의하세요!!
contents.ja: If you do not get the stars for a certain time, the combo will be cut off.
contents.zh: If you do not get the stars for a certain time, the combo will be cut off.

contents.en: Now it's time to explain the items.
contents.ja: Now it's time to explain the items.
contents.zh: Now it's time to explain the items.

contents.en: If you get items, you'll be able to research more stars safely.
contents.ko: 아이템을 획득하면 더 많은 별을 안전하게 조사할 수 있을 거에요.
contents.ja: If you get items, you'll be able to research more stars safely.
contents.zh: If you get items, you'll be able to research more stars safely.

contents.en: First of all, it's a star barrier that changes ice crystals into stars.
contents.ko: 먼저 눈결정을 별로 바꿔주는 별 방어막이에요.
contents.ja: First of all, it's a star barrier that changes ice crystals into stars.
contents.zh: First of all, it's a star barrier that changes ice crystals into stars.

contents.en: The next is a coin barrier that changes ice crystals into coins.
contents.ko: 다음은 눈결정을 코인 바꿔주는 코인 방어막이에요.
contents.ja: The next is a coin barrier that changes ice crystals into coins.
contents.zh: The next is a coin barrier that changes ice crystals into coins.

contents.en: Remember that you can upgrade your item ability with coins.
contents.ko: 코인으로 아이템 능력을 업그레이드 시킬수도 있다는 사실도 꼭 기억하세요.
contents.ja: Remember that you can upgrade your item ability with coins.
contents.zh: Remember that you can upgrade your item ability with coins.

contents.en: Oh, ice crystals are coming from everywhere!!
contents.ko: 이런, 사방에서 얼음 결정이 날아 오고 있어요!!
contents.ja: Oh, ice crystals are coming from everywhere!!
contents.zh: Oh, ice crystals are coming from everywhere!!

contents.en: I think It can show the ability of the barrier!!
contents.ko: 보호막의 능력을 보여줄 수 있을 것 같네요!
contents.ja: I think It can show the ability of the barrier!!
contents.zh: I think It can show the ability of the barrier!!

contents.en: Obtain a barrier to overcome the danger.

contents.zh: Obtain a barrier to overcome the danger.

contents.en:
It's a giant potion! 
When it gets bigger, the ice crystals will not be scary anymore!
contents.ko:
거대화 물약이에요! 
거대해지면 얼음결정이 더 이상 무섭지 않을거에요!

It's a giant potion!

contents.en: But be careful as soon as you get back to the origin size!
contents.ko: 하지만 곧 다시 원상태로 돌아오니까 주의하세요!
contents.ja: But be careful as soon as you get back to the origin size!
contents.zh: But be careful as soon as you get back to the origin size!

contents.ko: 튜토리얼을 다시 보고 싶다면 설정에서 다시보기 버튼을 눌러주세요.

contents.zh: If you want to see the tutorial again, please click the 'Replay Tutorial' button in the setting view.
